### LINUX ESSENTIALS ###
-------------------------------------
$ fastfetch	(system info)
-------------------------------------
$ btop	(system info)
-------------------------------------
$ ncdu <storage name>	(storage info)
-------------------------------------
$ tldr	(simplified apps manual)
-------------------------------------
$ clean	(system cleaner)
aur:
  git clone https://aur.archlinux.org/clean.git
  cd clean
  makepkg -si
github:
  git clone https://github.com/architalia/clean.git
  cd clean
  makepkg -si
-------------------------------------
$ nwg-look	(theme app)
-------------------------------------
$ tumbler	(thumbnail fix)
-------------------------------------
$ azote		(wallpaper picker)
* install swaybg first*
-------------------------------------
$ hyprshot	(screenshot)
  create bind: bind = $mainMod, PRINT, exec, hyprshot -m window
    Examples:
  capture a window                      `hyprshot -m window`
  capture active window to clipboard    `hyprshot -m window -m active --clipboard-only`
  capture selected monitor              `hyprshot -m output -m DP-1`
-------------------------------------
$ googler	(google search cli)
-------------------------------------
$ mlocate/plocate
$ updatedb
$ locate "whatever"
